BEAT VERSION Section::::East Side Beat version .
In 1991 , Italian dance music group East Side Beat remixed " Ride Like the Wind " in a style typical of early 1990s dance music .
There are five remixes in total .
Two versions are found on the 7 " single and an additional three are on the CD single .
The Factory Edit was included in FFRR Records ' " Only for the Headstrong " compilation album released in 1992 .
