VERSION Section::::Laurent Wery version .
Belgian DJ Laurent Wéry released a cover version of the song , which features vocals from Joss Mendosah .
The song was produced by Laurent Wery .
It was released in Belgium as a digital download on March 30 , 2013 .
The song peaked at number 26 in Belgium .
MUSIC VIDEO Section::::Music video .
A music video to accompany the release of " Ride Like the Wind " was first released on YouTube on April 8 , 2013 at a total length of two minutes and fifty - four seconds .
